         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg><seg rend="left"><pb facs="0023_FL81799781"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><date>7. X. 910</date></seg></seg><seg><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb68">Wien XVIII.</rs></hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><subst><del rend="strikethrough"><hi rend="pre-print">Spoettelgasse 7</hi></del><add place="below"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">Sternwartestr 71</rs></add></subst></seg><salute>lieber Herr Doctor,</salute></opener><p>am <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03795-1"/><rs type="event" ref="#pmb296492" subtype="implied"><date>Din<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Abend</time></rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03795-1"><ref type="schnitzler-kultur" target="pmb296492" subtype="See"/>. </note>, <add place="above">vor</add> 7 Uhr
               will uns <rs type="person" ref="#pmb13055"><hi rend="latintype">Wasserma<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c></hi></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eine neuen <rs type="work" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb76946">Einakter</rs>
               vorle<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en; ich bitte Sie, in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>einem, und un<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>erm Namen herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t dabei zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein.</p><closer>Ihr<lb/><signed>A. S.</signed></closer></div>
